  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105990/extras/5f28278209b02892818888f82448bc68.avif?t=1678848973\" width=615 height=346 /></span><br><strong>Lovebirb</strong> is a rhythm-based dating game about finding love one date at a time. Go on Bumbirb and swipe away to meet <strong>hot</strong> and <strong>single</strong> birbs in your area! Impress them by showing your best moves to the beat of the music. Sometimes you’ll succeed. Sometimes... it gets a little <i>awkward</i>. But fret not! You have plenty of chances to find your perfect tempo. So keep swiping!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A one-of-a-kind dating experience! 💖</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Lots of interesting and lovely birbs 🦆</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The sweetest tunes to dance to 🎵</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105990/extras/7e53652d840e992c20baa4bff9ceaef0.avif?t=1678848973\" width=600 height=167 /></span>",
